### Register user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testclient@example.com",
  "password": "client123"
}

### Test login with Basic Auth
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/1
Authorization: Basic dGVzdGNsaWVudEBleGFtcGxlLmNvbTpjbGllbnQxMjM=

### Get user by email (requires Basic Auth)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/email?email=testclient@example.com
Authorization: Basic dGVzdGNsaWVudEBleGFtcGxlLmNvbTpjbGllbnQxMjM=

### Add fuel entry for logged-in user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/fuel_entries
Authorization: Basic dGVzdGNsaWVudEBleGFtcGxlLmNvbTpjbGllbnQxMjM=
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": 1,
  "dateTime": "2025-11-18T15:01:00",
  "litres": 40.5,
  "odometer": 12345,
  "pricePerLitre": 1.95,
  "totalPrice": 79.0,
  "location": "Shell Helsinki",
  "notes": "Testi",
  "fullTank": true
}

### Get all fuel entries for logged-in user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/fuel_entries
Authorization: Basic dGVzdGNsaWVudEBleGFtcGxlLmNvbTpjbGllbnQxMjM=
